# Skill checkpoints get rewritten on every pre-commit /bugcheck run,
# so two branches with non-overlapping real diffs still conflict on
# `updated_at` and `skill_state.last_run.at`. The opchain-checkpoint
# driver parses the JSON, takes the newer side for telemetry fields,
# and only raises a conflict on real content collisions. See
# scripts/merge-checkpoint.mjs.
.checkpoints/*.checkpoint.json merge=opchain-checkpoint
